## Data Erasure

- Implement automated data erasure workflows
- Provide donor self-service deletion
- Audit all data access and modifications
- Maintain deletion logs for compliance

## Security Best Practices

- Use parameterized queries to prevent SQL injection
- Implement proper CORS policies
- Use Content Security Policy headers
- Regular security audits and penetration testing
- Monitor for suspicious activities

## Fundraising-Specific Security

- Protect donor financial information
- Implement proper call recording compliance
- Secure voice data and transcripts
- Handle sensitive campaign data appropriately
